ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN SUBSURFACE LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of subsurface lands in order to facilitate the development of a hydro power generating plant near BLUEFISH LAKE, and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made in 1949 (P.C. 3417 of July 13, 1949).
